### ============================================
### EMPTY/MISSING FIELDS - REQUIRED VALIDATION
### ============================================
### Tests with missing or empty required fields
### Change @language to 'vi' to test in Vietnamese
### ============================================

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/v1
@contentType = application/json
@email = test.signup@example.com
@password = SecurePass123!@#
@fullName = Nguyen Van Test User
@gender = male
@birthday = 1995-06-15
# @language = en
@language = vi

### ============================================
### SEND OTP - MISSING FIELDS
### ============================================

### Missing Email Field
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup/send-otp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept-Language: {{language}}

{
}

###

### Empty Email
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup/send-otp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept-Language: {{language}}

